data.comment: The first-half is in progress. Seongnam get the game underway.
Seongnam to take a throw-in in Suwon Bluewings territory.
In the minute 2, Ball safe as Suwon Bluewings is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Free kick for Suwon Bluewings in the half of Seongnam.
Suwon Bluewings's Ko Seung-beom is on target but unsuccessful.
In the minute 7, Seongnam pushes forward through Tomislav Kis, whose finish on goal is saved.
Kim Gun-hee is on target to give Suwon Bluewings a 1-0 advantage.
Kim Woo-sung signals a free kick to Seongnam in their own half.
In the minute 14, Kim Woo-sung awards Suwon Bluewings a goal kick.
Free kick Suwon Bluewings.
In Suwon Seongnam drive forward through Im Seung-kyeom. His shot is on target but it's saved.
In the minute 17, In Suwon a free kick has been awarded the away team.
Na Sangho grabs a goal to bring things level at 1-1 at Suwon World Cup Stadium.
Kim Woo-sung signals a free kick to Seongnam.
In the minute 22, Can Suwon Bluewings capitalize from this dangerous free kick?
Kim Woo-sung awards the away team a throw-in.
Free kick for Seongnam in their own half.
In the minute 29, Throw-in for Suwon Bluewings in the half of Seongnam.
Free kick in a good position for Suwon Bluewings!
Seongnam awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 32, Free kick for Suwon Bluewings in the half of Seongnam.
Can Suwon Bluewings get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Seongnam's half?
Kim Woo-sung signals a free kick to Suwon Bluewings just outside Seongnam's area.
In the minute 36, Seongnam have a dangerous throw-in.
Free kick Suwon Bluewings.
Kim Woo-sung signals a free kick to Suwon Bluewings in their own half.
In the minute 38, Seongnam awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In Suwon a free kick has been awarded the away team.
Suwon Bluewings have a goal kick.
In the minute 41, Throw-in for Seongnam in their own half.
Suwon Bluewings drives forward and Kim Min-woo gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
Throw-in for Suwon Bluewings at Suwon World Cup Stadium.
In the minute 43, It's getting dangerous! Free kick for Suwon Bluewings close to the penalty box.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Suwon.
Im Seung-kyeom (Seongnam) has received a first yellow card.
In the minute 45, Throw-in Suwon Bluewings.
The 1st half is prolonged by 1 minutes of added time.
Kim Woo-sung signals a Suwon Bluewings throw-in in Seongnam's half.
In the minute 45, The first-half has ended.
The ref has blown to start the second-half. Suwon Bluewings kick-off.
Ball goes out of play for a Seongnam goal kick.
In the minute 48, Goal kick for Seongnam at Suwon World Cup Stadium.
Throw-in for Seongnam at Suwon World Cup Stadium.
In the minute 50, Kim Woo-sung signals a free kick to Suwon Bluewings.
At Suwon World Cup Stadium, Yeon Je-un has been yellow-carded for the away team.
Suwon Bluewings's Ko Seung-beom misses with an attempt on goal.
Throw-in Suwon Bluewings.
In the minute 55, Yeom Ki-hun is replacing Park Sang-hyeok for the home team.
The away team replace Park Tae-jun with Hong Si-hoo.
Kim Woo-sung signals a free kick to Seongnam.
In the minute 61, It's a goal kick for the home team in Suwon.
Suwon Bluewings awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Throw-in for Seongnam in their own half.
In the minute 66, Goal kick for Seongnam at Suwon World Cup Stadium.
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Throw-in for Seongnam in the half of Suwon Bluewings.
In the minute 68, Corner awarded to Seongnam.
Kim Woo-sung awards Suwon Bluewings a goal kick.
In the minute 69, Kim Woo-sung awards the home team a throw-in.
The away team have replaced Lee Tae-heui with Seo Bo-min. This is the second substitution made today by Nam Il Kim.
Han Seok-hee for Suwon Bluewings is whistled offside.
Seongnam awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 71, Lee Lim Saeng (Suwon Bluewings) is making a second substitution, with Adam Taggart replacing Han Seok-hee.
An attacking Seongnam player has been brought down in the area - penalty!
Tomislav Kis nets and Seongnam now lead 1-2. The goal came from the penalty spot.
In the minute 79, Ball safe as Seongnam is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Free kick for Seongnam in their own half.
Can Suwon Bluewings get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Seongnam's half?
In the minute 81, Seongnam awarded a free kick in their own half.
Free kick for Seongnam in their own half.
Adam Taggart for Suwon Bluewings gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
Ball goes out of play for a Seongnam goal kick.
In the minute 84, Kim Hyeon-seong is replacing Tomislav Kis for Seongnam at Suwon World Cup Stadium.
Suwon Bluewings have been awarded a corner by Kim Woo-sung.
In the minute 87, Suwon Bluewings's Ko Seung-beom gets in a shot on goal at Suwon World Cup Stadium. But the effort is unsuccessful.
Seongnam have a goal kick.
Suwon Bluewings are in shooting range from this free kick.
Throw-in for Suwon Bluewings close to the penalty box.
At Suwon World Cup Stadium the fourth official shows that 4 minutes will be added to the 2nd half.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Kim Woo-sung signals a free kick to Seongnam in their own half.
Suwon Bluewings's Yeom Ki-hun is on target but unsuccessful.
Throw-in Suwon Bluewings.
Free kick Suwon Bluewings.
Corner awarded to Suwon Bluewings.
Full-time! The final score is 1-2.
